        <p class="mb-4">Beyond your logo, our <a href="/design-services/graphic-design" class="link-notification">graphic design</a> team creates full layouts for any print application, flyers, banner artwork, event programs, and more. Your logo will also be digitized for <a href="/custom-apparel/printing-options/embroidery" class="link-notification">embroidery</a> on polos, caps, and jackets, not just printing. And a strong logo is the starting point for <a href="/vehicle-graphics" class="link-notification">vehicle graphics</a> that command attention on the road.</p>
        <p><a href="/" class="link-notification">Top 5 Percent</a> delivers your final logo in all formats you will need, vector files for print production, PNG files for digital use, and specific format packages for any production process we use for your signage or apparel. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to discuss your logo design project today.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
